organization.title: NHS Kent and Medway
organization.description:
NHS Eastern and Coastal Kent, NHS Medway, and NHS West Kent were jointly known as NHS Kent and Medway. They were all PCTs.

Primary Care Trusts ceased to exist in April 2013, following the Health and Social Care Act 2012. The 152 PCTs' responsibilities for were transferred to 211 new "clinical commissioning groups".
